  "description": "Flavio loves Isabella but will their meddling Mothers rip their worlds apart or bring them together? Clever servants, a braggart Capitano, a fortune teller weave in and out to complicate this hilarious, scheme filled journey for the young lovers. A ZANY Renaissance Commedia dell’Arte musical romp with contemporary, fun flair!",
